  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educate 600 Women &amp; Girls in Kumbotso and Okehi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Women and Girls can be meaningful and supportive in all aspect of life. Once they are literate and skilled they become visible with voice. Regrettably we have many women and girls in Kumbotso and Okehi Local Government Areas of Kano and Kogi States, Nigeria that are illiterate, poor and marginalized. We need additional literacy and skill centres to provide basic literacy for 6 months as a foundation to 600 women and girls and train them on life skills that boost their status in 2 months.</narrative>
  </description>
